<p><strong>红薯粥</strong></p>
<p><strong>制作：</strong></p>
<p>1.红薯削皮切块。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181101/f3da986ef99041eabefae93339bd530d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>2.备好糙米、薏米、糯米和大米。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181101/56cf8bfa0a5b4cae9d78a3ef85dff32e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3.将四种米清洗干净后，和红薯块一起放入电锅中，加水大约1400毫升。</p>
<p>4.启动煮粥档，即可得到浓郁香稠的红薯粥。006</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181101/15b3adcc2af74fff88fee42e447a5ed4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>